{
  "page": "Tregar",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the Lysene merchant prince, see <a href=\"/index.php/Tregar_Ormollen\" title=\"Tregar Ormollen\">Tregar Ormollen</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Captain</span><br />Tregar</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Captain_of_the_guards\" title=\"Captain of the guards\">Captain of the guards</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Tregar</b> is the captain of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister_guards\" title=\"House Lannister guards\">guards</a> sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tregar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Tregar owns a helm with a <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lion</a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crest_(heraldry)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Crest (heraldry)\">crest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tregar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tregar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Tregar is the captain of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister_guards\" title=\"House Lannister guards\">Lannister guards</a> that are with Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> when Jaime confronts Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> in the streets of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Eddard severely injures Tregar in the ensuing fight, and he dies five days after the fight.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tregar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Vylarr\" title=\"Vylarr\">Vylarr</a> has succeeded Tregar as captain of the red cloaks in the capital.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n